    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">Going treasure hunting? Then you need the ASR Outdoor 8.5&quot; Green Sand Scooper! This sand scooper is super lightweight, making it ideal for scooping up sand to shake out treasures on dry, sandy beaches. Since it&#039;s constructed of durable plastic, it wont interfere with your metal detector making it easier to find treasure. Simply use your metal detector to locate the target area, scoop up some sand in the target area and run the metal detector over the scoop. Then, gently shake the scoop side to side, allowing the sand to fall out of the holes and uncover the treasure. Make sure you have one of these before your next treasure hunt!</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Outdoor Large Mineral Gold Prospecting Pay Dirt Hand Trowel</h2>\n  <p>Going treasure hunting? Then you need the ASR Outdoor 8.5&quot; Green Sand Scooper!</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>ASR Outdoor Sand Scoop - Green Color</li>\n    <li><strong>Length:</strong> 8.5&quot;</li>\n    <li>Built in lanyard hole in handle, made from heavy duty ABS plastic, will not give off any false positive readings from your metal detector</li>\n    <li><strong>Capacity:</strong> 3 Quarts, Hole Size: 0.5 inch, Number of holes: 78</li>\n    <li>Ideal for beach combing, metal detector accessory, gold panning, treasure hunting and gardening</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/sports_outdoors/gold_panning/accessories/GP3-SS20_Green_Sand_Scoop_Stock1.jpg\" alt=\"Going treasure hunting\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> ASRO8GG12-172</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 819673966779</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> Large</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>This sand scooper is super lightweight, making it ideal for scooping up sand to shake out treasures on dry, sandy beaches. Since it&#039;s constructed of durable plastic, it wont interfere with your metal detector making it easier to find treasure.</p>\n  <p>Simply use your metal detector to locate the target area, scoop up some sand in the target area and run the metal detector over the scoop. Then, gently shake the scoop side to side, allowing the sand to fall out of the holes and uncover the treasure. Make sure you have one of these before your next treasure hunt!</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
